HAC ENC is an app which enables all the users of Croatian motorways to check toll price or traffic conditions. Electronic toll collection is a contactless toll collection method used on all Croatian motorways. Use this app to find the closest HAC retail place where you can buy your ETC device and save money while using Croatian motorways.
